Volunteer for human phase-shifting experiement, for military deployment

Experiments start with simple orientation:
  Basic movement
  Test features

Get given the phase shifter device
  Basic phase shifting
  Advanced phase shifting

Enemies:
Enemies are equipped with lasers. Lasers don't do damage but getting hit incurs a point loss (or gain, if we go Golf style).
  Sentries:
    Automatic
    Stationary/mounted track
    Fast, but limited

  Infantry
    Slow
    Distractable
      How?
    Moveable

  Advice Drone
    Follows you around
    Has a blinking light, like a camera
    Gives you "advice"
    Potential extra bit: Phases to get around obstacles to keep following you?
